WEBVTT

01:37.920 --> 01:41.060
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.100 --> 01:43.990
[Episode 18]

01:47.310 --> 01:47.870
Mr. Ji,

01:47.870 --> 01:48.759
Ms. Xu is here.

01:49.320 --> 01:49.920
Let her in.

01:56.950 --> 01:58.479
Do you know why I called you here?

01:58.479 --> 01:59.120
Yes.

02:00.740 --> 02:02.940
Because the morning shoot was delayed.

02:03.150 --> 02:04.430
Delayed?

02:06.690 --> 02:08.490
I specifically reminded you
the day before,

02:08.490 --> 02:10.430
and repeatedly stressed that
the crew

02:10.430 --> 02:11.150
would arrive at 8:00.

02:11.150 --> 02:12.470
What time did you arrive?

02:12.470 --> 02:13.310
Xu Miyu,

02:13.310 --> 02:14.600
as a forewoman,

02:14.630 --> 02:16.590
can you not even fulfill
such a simple request

02:16.590 --> 02:17.430
from a guest?

02:17.430 --> 02:18.630
I arrived at 7:30

02:19.750 --> 02:20.870
and kept reminding them.

02:20.870 --> 02:22.180
What's the use of just reminding them?

02:22.180 --> 02:23.460
David already said it—

02:23.490 --> 02:24.400
there was so much luggage

02:24.400 --> 02:25.960
piled up in the presidential suite,

02:25.960 --> 02:28.340
and the butlers were going in and out,
yet no one cleaned it up.

02:28.340 --> 02:29.329
Ultimately,

02:29.400 --> 02:31.930
the delay was caused
by your irresponsible service.

02:31.930 --> 02:33.770
The guest had 14 suitcases in total.

02:33.770 --> 02:34.750
Every suitcase

02:34.750 --> 02:36.610
was filled with her private clothes
and personal items.

02:36.610 --> 02:38.390
Without the guest's permission,

02:38.390 --> 02:40.000
we cannot touch any of that luggage.

02:40.000 --> 02:41.960
Couldn't you have just asked David?

02:41.960 --> 02:44.160
I couldn't reach him all day yesterday.

02:45.480 --> 02:46.640
Mr. Ji,

02:47.120 --> 02:47.750
with this attitude of hers,

02:47.750 --> 02:49.470
I really can't work with her.

02:49.470 --> 02:50.160
Besides,

02:51.000 --> 02:52.780
Qiao Feifei has been contacting me.

02:52.780 --> 02:54.190
I should have first
arranged a VIP parking space

02:54.190 --> 02:55.840
and the massage package for her.

02:55.840 --> 02:57.070
If it really doesn't work out, I...

02:57.070 --> 02:58.130
Come to me anytime.

03:18.100 --> 03:19.630
Do you feel wronged?

03:20.260 --> 03:20.890
No.

03:22.640 --> 03:23.990
But I did look for David.

03:24.010 --> 03:24.760
I couldn't find him.

03:24.760 --> 03:26.760
We are not discussing

03:26.780 --> 03:28.130
whether a room butler

03:28.160 --> 03:29.880
should tell a guest in advance

03:29.900 --> 03:32.110
to prepare their clothes for the next day,

03:32.110 --> 03:34.470
nor are we judging
whether you actually did enough

03:34.470 --> 03:35.870
from yesterday until now.

03:35.870 --> 03:36.550
Because

03:36.910 --> 03:38.470
it has already happened.

03:40.020 --> 03:41.610
When facing a problem,

03:41.680 --> 03:42.710
don't waste your time

03:42.710 --> 03:44.520
dwelling on emotions.

03:44.540 --> 03:45.780
Instead, you should quickly

03:45.780 --> 03:47.970
find a solution.

03:48.990 --> 03:50.440
Truly good service

03:50.460 --> 03:52.560
isn't just acting polite.

03:52.690 --> 03:56.350
It's about having the real ability
to solve problems decisively.

04:02.930 --> 04:03.770
I understand.

04:11.770 --> 04:12.400
Recently,

04:12.400 --> 04:14.400
the famous actress Li Bingyan,
who had retired for years,

04:14.400 --> 04:15.580
has gone public with her relationship.

04:15.580 --> 04:16.950
At the Purong Hotel in Shanghai,

04:16.950 --> 04:18.560
she showed affection
with her younger boyfriend,

04:18.560 --> 04:20.160
causing heated discussions among netizens.

04:20.160 --> 04:21.430
Originally participating alone

04:21.430 --> 04:22.070
in the show "Begin Again",

04:22.070 --> 04:23.040
she

04:23.040 --> 04:25.070
now has to be accompanied by an assistant

04:25.070 --> 04:26.270
and escorted by security.

04:26.270 --> 04:27.720
Her net worth skyrocketed overnight.

04:27.720 --> 04:28.450
It is said that

04:28.450 --> 04:29.800
the show's production team
has already designated her

04:29.800 --> 04:32.200
as a regular guest
for the next two seasons.

04:33.840 --> 04:34.570
Zhenzhen,

04:35.680 --> 04:37.270
when you begged me

04:37.390 --> 04:38.480
to bring our Feifei

04:38.480 --> 04:39.940
to stay at your Purong,

04:40.600 --> 04:42.260
I believed in your sincerity.

04:42.510 --> 04:43.770
But what is the result?

04:44.000 --> 04:45.430
I put in so much effort

04:45.720 --> 04:48.050
to arrange media exposure for our Feifei.

04:48.120 --> 04:51.270
In one instant, it was all stolen
by that person surnamed Li.

04:51.270 --> 04:53.770
Just like that,
their side gained countless new followers.

04:53.770 --> 04:55.120
Our Feifei's star power,

04:55.120 --> 04:56.820
the kind that can stir up huge traffic,

04:56.820 --> 04:59.200
is not meant to be someone else's
stepping stone.

04:59.200 --> 05:01.000
Tell me, as a top sales rep,

05:01.160 --> 05:02.360
how do you do your job?

05:02.510 --> 05:03.360
I'm sorry.

05:04.120 --> 05:05.800
It's already good enough
that I didn't go looking for you.

05:05.800 --> 05:07.120
How dare you come over here

05:07.120 --> 05:09.010
and talk to me about a fan meet-and-greet?

05:09.010 --> 05:10.050
Do you think

05:10.160 --> 05:11.830
there's any chance
of us cooperating again?

05:11.830 --> 05:13.690
Wei, I'm really sorry.

05:13.720 --> 05:14.820
Really sorry.

05:14.850 --> 05:16.310
I'm sorry.

05:16.560 --> 05:17.800
I need to take a call.

05:24.990 --> 05:25.840
Got it.

05:25.870 --> 05:26.550
I'm coming.

05:32.680 --> 05:33.830
Calm down, Wei.

05:33.900 --> 05:34.830
I'll find another chance

05:34.830 --> 05:36.870
to win one back for Feifei.

05:36.890 --> 05:38.330
Don't you trust me?

05:51.060 --> 05:51.940
Ms. Lu.

05:52.000 --> 05:53.200
Mr. Ji wants to see me.

05:56.390 --> 05:57.880
[General Manager's Office]

06:02.800 --> 06:03.270
Come in.

06:05.480 --> 06:07.390
Sorry, I'm late.

06:07.600 --> 06:08.200
Come here.

06:10.870 --> 06:12.070
Let me introduce you.

06:12.070 --> 06:12.950
This is

06:13.000 --> 06:13.800
Ms. Brown,

06:13.800 --> 06:14.850
the Commercial Director

06:14.850 --> 06:15.720
of Liberty Group.

06:15.720 --> 06:16.720
You're the woman

06:16.720 --> 06:18.120
who inspired Marcos, aren't you?

06:18.120 --> 06:19.270
You're amazing.

06:19.270 --> 06:20.360
You know that he wouldn't stop
speaking about you

06:20.360 --> 06:22.800
until I came here.

06:23.470 --> 06:23.980
Please.

06:24.000 --> 06:24.730
Thank you.

06:25.640 --> 06:28.370
As everything I should have done,

06:28.390 --> 06:31.610
I always put my clients' demands first,

06:31.720 --> 06:35.120
and we're honored to
reach Marcos' standards.

06:35.159 --> 06:36.360
I promise

06:36.360 --> 06:38.720
we will continue to provide
the best service

06:38.720 --> 06:42.040
to you and members of your company.

06:42.240 --> 06:43.270
Thank you.

06:43.600 --> 06:44.270
Oh.

06:44.680 --> 06:49.390
Let me extend Marcos' gratitude from him.

06:49.760 --> 06:50.810
If I may?

06:50.840 --> 06:51.640
It's yours.

06:51.720 --> 06:52.600
Thank you.

06:56.720 --> 06:57.800
Dear Ms. Xu,

06:58.680 --> 06:59.600
I feel so lucky

06:59.600 --> 07:02.260
to have enjoyed
your incredible butler service

07:02.300 --> 07:05.240
at Purong Hotel in Shanghai, China.

07:06.120 --> 07:08.030
My visit to the archives before leaving

07:08.030 --> 07:10.830
was the highlight
of my entire trip to China.

07:10.900 --> 07:13.120
Thanks for your insight and warmth,

07:13.120 --> 07:14.560
making me feel your genuine service

07:14.560 --> 07:16.120
and care.

07:16.610 --> 07:18.000
I hope my team

07:18.000 --> 07:20.800
can enjoy your
amazing hospitality in the future.

07:21.390 --> 07:24.240
Yours sincerely, Marcos Yang.

07:27.180 --> 07:29.120
It is my pleasure.

07:29.120 --> 07:30.680
You deserve it.

07:32.110 --> 07:35.040
Thanks to Marcos and you.

07:37.780 --> 07:39.130
Thank you so much.

07:47.710 --> 07:55.930
[Internal Office] [Convention Center]

07:49.450 --> 07:50.720
I'm looking forward for a strong

07:50.720 --> 07:52.980
and long cooperation.

07:53.120 --> 07:55.240
I'm flattered, honestly.

07:56.680 --> 07:59.460
Ms. Xu, it's very nice to meet you.

07:59.610 --> 08:01.160
Hope to see you again.

08:01.160 --> 08:02.920
Definitely. We've just signed the contract

08:02.920 --> 08:05.050
so you will definitely see me again.

08:05.720 --> 08:07.800
I'm looking forward
to this great service

08:07.800 --> 08:09.240
next time I come.

08:09.240 --> 08:10.480
Thank you very much.

08:10.750 --> 08:11.480
Thank you.

08:11.760 --> 08:12.560
Secretary Wu,

08:12.830 --> 08:13.490
see her out.

08:13.650 --> 08:14.130
Okay.

08:14.160 --> 08:15.360
-Thank you.
-Okay.

08:15.980 --> 08:21.350
[Internal Office] [Convention Center]

08:24.600 --> 08:25.360
Mr. Ji,

08:25.520 --> 08:26.360
I also put a lot of effort

08:26.360 --> 08:28.000
into this order.

08:28.130 --> 08:30.160
I didn't mean to steal Ms. Xu's credit.

08:30.160 --> 08:30.860
Post card.

08:33.179 --> 08:36.390
[Internal Office] [Convention Center]

09:33.220 --> 09:34.400
Can you handle it well?

09:34.400 --> 09:35.450
I can.

09:35.730 --> 09:37.330
I'll trust you one more time.

09:38.110 --> 09:39.590
Did you arrange

09:39.620 --> 09:41.260
these dishes?

09:41.280 --> 09:42.720
I'm glad you like them.

09:43.440 --> 09:45.450
I don't care what ingredients you use.

09:45.450 --> 09:46.590
If this noodle dish fails,

09:46.590 --> 09:47.640
will you take responsibility?

09:47.640 --> 09:48.450
I will.

09:51.390 --> 09:52.120
Actually,

09:52.290 --> 09:53.550
your butler is also

09:53.550 --> 09:55.170
an excellent chef.

09:55.270 --> 09:57.630
Today's plain noodles were made by her.

09:57.660 --> 09:59.240
I really finished

09:59.360 --> 10:01.600
the plain noodles.

10:03.270 --> 10:04.030
With an attitude like hers,

10:04.030 --> 10:05.720
I really can't work with her.

10:05.740 --> 10:07.100
If it really doesn't work out, I...

10:07.100 --> 10:08.230
Contact me anytime.

10:10.680 --> 10:11.890
Postcard.

10:23.080 --> 10:24.700
If you want to be like before,

10:24.840 --> 10:27.440
you have to live more
strongly than anyone else.

10:27.440 --> 10:28.740
You have to learn how to climb higher,

10:28.740 --> 10:30.410
learn how to fight,
and learn how to take what's yours.

10:30.410 --> 10:31.840
You must make everyone
who looked down on you

10:30.610 --> 10:33.710
[Young Lu Zhenzhen]

10:31.840 --> 10:32.720
regret it!

10:33.010 --> 10:34.010
Understand?

11:01.680 --> 11:03.310
Regarding the fan meeting,

11:03.340 --> 11:05.760
the agency has no intention
of cooperating,

11:05.760 --> 11:07.420
so I'm afraid I have to apologize.

11:07.420 --> 11:08.450
Ms. Lu,

11:08.510 --> 11:09.860
can you let us go upstairs

11:09.860 --> 11:11.160
to see Feifei just once?

11:11.160 --> 11:12.280
Name your price.

11:12.630 --> 11:14.880
Feifei is a very important client of mine.

11:14.880 --> 11:16.960
How could I ruin my career

11:16.980 --> 11:18.380
for a little money?

11:18.660 --> 11:19.570
Then, Ms. Lu,

11:19.590 --> 11:21.540
is Li Bingyan also your important client?

11:21.540 --> 11:22.530
What do you mean?

11:23.120 --> 11:25.120
We're just worried about Feifei.

11:25.140 --> 11:26.540
That Li is not popular,

11:26.570 --> 11:27.750
but she loves to clout-chase.

11:27.750 --> 11:29.500
Our Feifei is beautiful and kind,

11:29.500 --> 11:30.790
and can't do anything to her.

11:30.790 --> 11:32.330
But as her fans,

11:32.600 --> 11:34.530
we have an obligation
to get justice for her.

11:34.530 --> 11:35.330
That's right.

11:35.440 --> 11:37.350
We promise not to disturb Sister Feifei,

11:37.350 --> 11:38.950
but we must get revenge.

11:40.190 --> 11:42.330
You three can't go up
to the presidential suite.

11:42.330 --> 11:43.510
You need to swipe a card to go up,

11:43.510 --> 11:45.120
and you also need to register.

11:45.120 --> 11:47.930
Especially since two big stars
are staying up there right now,

11:47.930 --> 11:49.710
the security is very strict.

11:50.650 --> 11:52.330
Ms. Lu, you are very resourceful.

11:52.330 --> 11:54.090
We all think you're amazing.

11:54.120 --> 11:55.180
You must have a way.

11:56.480 --> 11:57.720
I really don't have a way.

11:57.720 --> 11:58.630
I'm sorry.

11:59.590 --> 12:02.040
You must have a way, Ms. Lu.

12:03.240 --> 12:05.600
Otherwise, how could you become

12:05.600 --> 12:07.870
the VIP Account Manager of Purong Hotel?

12:07.990 --> 12:08.860
Exactly.

12:09.900 --> 12:11.650
You three are quite sweet-talkers,

12:11.650 --> 12:14.710
and your intelligence gathering
is quite impressive.

12:18.000 --> 12:19.480
Seeing that you have such deep sisterhood

12:19.480 --> 12:20.720
with your sister,

12:20.720 --> 12:21.960
I can help you.

12:22.280 --> 12:23.230
But promise me,

12:23.480 --> 12:25.610
not to mention my name to anyone.

12:25.930 --> 12:27.290
We promise not to tell.

12:34.280 --> 12:39.160
[Duan Aoxiang, 1825]

12:42.960 --> 12:43.840
If we handle him,

12:43.840 --> 12:46.040
can we get into the presidential suite?

12:47.870 --> 12:50.010
We'll check into the
executive floor
right away.

12:50.010 --> 12:50.930
Let's go.

12:57.080 --> 12:57.840
Hello.

13:10.010 --> 13:11.040
Daniel.

13:11.250 --> 13:12.390
Where are you going? Going out?

13:12.390 --> 13:13.450
I'm going on a date.

13:14.080 --> 13:15.000
Who are you dating?

13:15.000 --> 13:16.600
Why not invite him to your hotel room?

13:16.600 --> 13:17.720
What are you doing?

13:17.740 --> 13:18.860
Did Old Madam send you

13:18.860 --> 13:20.020
to spy on me?

13:20.040 --> 13:20.920
No.

13:21.000 --> 13:23.400
I'm just afraid you'll miss your medicine.

13:24.630 --> 13:25.430
Don't worry.

13:25.750 --> 13:26.200
Ming,

13:26.200 --> 13:27.960
my old friend, is back from Shenzhen.

13:27.960 --> 13:29.300
I'm going to see him.

13:30.000 --> 13:30.750
Take it easy.

13:43.600 --> 13:45.240
Behind you!

13:46.630 --> 13:48.830
Bro, do you know how to defend the tower?

13:50.080 --> 13:50.800
Seriously…

13:50.840 --> 13:52.000
Are you stupid?

14:01.330 --> 14:02.120
Mr. Duan.

14:03.120 --> 14:03.960
Run!

14:03.960 --> 14:05.240
You can't beat him.

14:05.720 --> 14:07.000
Someone is watching you.

14:07.000 --> 14:08.080
Where?

14:08.080 --> 14:10.340
The direction is from your four o'clock.

14:21.200 --> 14:23.380
It looks like the other side disconnected.

14:23.380 --> 14:24.310
Does it?

14:25.440 --> 14:26.960
Did you get a clear look?

14:27.000 --> 14:28.600
Is he really Duan Aoxiang?

14:28.600 --> 14:30.080
Yes.

14:30.510 --> 14:32.300
Am I this popular now?

14:34.750 --> 14:35.240
Duan...

14:35.480 --> 14:36.000
Duan...

14:36.120 --> 14:36.720
Duan...

14:36.750 --> 14:38.240
Duan Aoxiang!

14:38.240 --> 14:39.220
Who are you?

14:39.250 --> 14:40.590
Who sent you to tail me?

14:43.050 --> 14:44.210
We...

14:44.240 --> 14:46.160
We weren't sent to tail you.

14:46.190 --> 14:47.990
We are Qiao Feifei's fans.

14:48.120 --> 14:49.750
We want to go upstairs to find Li Bingyan

14:49.750 --> 14:50.840
to avenge Feifei.

14:51.360 --> 14:52.600
We need your help.

14:53.850 --> 14:56.250
Qiao Feifei's fans

14:56.280 --> 14:57.820
came to find Li Bingyan?

15:00.320 --> 15:01.120
Interesting.

15:03.320 --> 15:04.290
Ms. Xu.

15:04.430 --> 15:06.360
Mr. Tan, are you here to see Daniel?

15:06.780 --> 15:08.310
I also dropped by to see you.

15:09.250 --> 15:11.320
I just went to my dad's room
to look for him.

15:11.320 --> 15:12.200
He doesn't seem to be here.

15:12.200 --> 15:13.600
Do you know where he went?

15:14.360 --> 15:16.130
Mr. Tan seems to have gone out.

15:16.150 --> 15:16.760
Did you

15:16.840 --> 15:18.000
call him?

15:18.200 --> 15:19.200
He went out?

15:20.360 --> 15:21.120
I called him,

15:21.120 --> 15:22.450
but he isn't answering.

15:24.240 --> 15:26.370
Could something have happened to him?

15:29.870 --> 15:30.720
Daniel!

15:32.240 --> 15:32.840
Dad!

15:33.890 --> 15:34.610
Daniel!

15:34.630 --> 15:35.470
Dad!

15:36.490 --> 15:38.290
It seems he hasn't returned yet.

15:39.000 --> 15:39.960
Where did he go?

15:39.960 --> 15:41.630
He hasn't answered his phone all day.

15:41.630 --> 15:43.150
Mr. Tan, don't worry.

15:43.620 --> 15:44.620
I remember

15:44.650 --> 15:46.190
Daniel said when he left this afternoon

15:46.190 --> 15:48.200
that he was going to
see a friend named Ming.

15:48.200 --> 15:49.510
Do you have Ming's phone number

15:49.510 --> 15:50.720
or his address?

15:51.480 --> 15:52.360
Ming?

15:53.000 --> 15:53.750
I don't.

15:54.120 --> 15:56.450
Wait, I think I've heard this name before.

15:57.720 --> 15:58.470
How about this?

15:58.470 --> 16:00.070
I'll give Aunt Wanjun a call.

16:01.840 --> 16:02.510
What?

16:02.750 --> 16:04.120
No one is at Ming's house.

16:04.120 --> 16:05.790
Mr. Tan, don't worry.

16:07.330 --> 16:08.870
I know a place

16:08.900 --> 16:10.900
that Mr. Tan mentioned to me before.

16:10.930 --> 16:11.600
Wait a moment.

16:11.600 --> 16:12.120
I'll come find you

16:12.120 --> 16:13.200
and take you there.

16:13.960 --> 16:15.390
You're on duty tonight.

16:16.000 --> 16:17.330
I need to go out for a bit.

16:17.470 --> 16:19.740
The presidential suite
has no special arrangements tonight.

16:19.740 --> 16:21.000
Don't go up there rashly.

16:21.000 --> 16:22.580
If there are any emergencies,

16:22.580 --> 16:23.510
contact me immediately.

16:23.510 --> 16:24.000
Okay.

16:25.030 --> 16:25.630
By the way,

16:26.240 --> 16:27.630
if Mr. Tan comes back,

16:27.630 --> 16:28.510
call me right away.

16:28.510 --> 16:29.000
Okay.

16:36.280 --> 16:37.040
Hello.

16:37.060 --> 16:38.860
Executive floor receptionist.

16:38.990 --> 16:39.770
Please wait a moment.

16:39.770 --> 16:40.900
I'll be right there.

17:09.440 --> 17:10.750
Thank you, Mr. Duan.

17:11.160 --> 17:12.220
Keep a low profile.

17:14.390 --> 17:15.079
Mr. Duan,

17:15.109 --> 17:16.160
are we really letting them go up?

17:16.160 --> 17:17.530
What if they cause trouble?

17:17.530 --> 17:19.640
Isn't it better if they cause trouble?

17:19.640 --> 17:21.720
Ji Feng gave me
this red carpet gift package.

17:21.720 --> 17:24.589
I was just worrying about
what to give him in return.

17:25.210 --> 17:26.030
Let's go.

17:26.089 --> 17:27.890
Let's go home and enjoy the show.

17:28.830 --> 17:30.220
Feifei is right here.

17:30.240 --> 17:31.240
Yes.

17:40.070 --> 17:42.000
We must find Li Bingyan today!

17:42.000 --> 17:43.000
Who are you?

17:43.510 --> 17:44.350
How did you get up here?

17:44.350 --> 17:45.280
It's Li Bingyan.

18:03.670 --> 18:04.670
Mr. Tan!

18:05.490 --> 18:06.140
Here.

18:07.310 --> 18:08.080
Sir,

18:08.110 --> 18:09.110
wake up.

18:09.400 --> 18:10.170
Sir.

18:10.240 --> 18:11.080
Dad.

18:11.480 --> 18:12.240
Dad.

18:12.550 --> 18:13.530
Dad, wake up.

18:13.590 --> 18:14.830
Is Mr. Tan alright?

18:15.790 --> 18:16.550
Sir,

18:16.710 --> 18:18.240
Get up and come home with me.

18:18.040 --> 18:23.090
[Luo Qingping]

18:18.440 --> 18:19.240
Wake up.

18:19.440 --> 18:20.210
Get up.

18:20.720 --> 18:21.680
Can you get up?

18:21.680 --> 18:22.240
Get up.

18:22.240 --> 18:23.240
We're going home.

18:32.600 --> 18:33.930
He is sleeping soundly.

18:36.830 --> 18:38.310
Thanks a lot for today.

18:39.120 --> 18:41.190
How did you know they'd go there?

18:41.970 --> 18:43.970
Mr. Tan mentioned to me before

18:44.000 --> 18:45.480
that there was a jazz bar

18:45.500 --> 18:46.460
he really liked.

18:46.620 --> 18:47.360
Right.

18:47.390 --> 18:48.880
The jazz band's first performance

18:48.880 --> 18:49.920
was also there.

18:49.920 --> 18:51.070
So I figured

18:51.070 --> 18:52.270
it must be that place.

18:53.920 --> 18:55.680
You haven't known my father for long,

18:55.680 --> 18:57.010
yet you know him so well.

18:57.190 --> 18:58.140
Unlike me,

18:58.210 --> 18:59.900
I've lived with him for so many years,

18:59.900 --> 19:02.030
but I act like an idiot.

19:02.590 --> 19:04.190
I don't know his past,

19:04.210 --> 19:05.600
nor his preferences.

19:05.810 --> 19:07.090
It's quite shameful.

19:08.050 --> 19:09.070
Don't say that.

19:09.290 --> 19:10.690
You are so busy with work.

19:13.000 --> 19:14.710
[Lu Zhenzhen]

19:15.760 --> 19:16.490
Hello?

19:21.380 --> 19:23.660
[Luo Qingping] [Lu Zhenzhen]

19:23.070 --> 19:23.880
What's wrong?

19:24.000 --> 19:24.730
Are you okay?

19:24.830 --> 19:26.490
I have so many missed calls.

19:26.530 --> 19:28.000
My phone was on silent.

19:28.020 --> 19:28.740
Oh no.

19:29.270 --> 19:31.310
Something must have happened at the hotel.

19:31.310 --> 19:32.110
Don't worry.

19:32.150 --> 19:32.780
Driver,

19:33.000 --> 19:33.550
please hurry.

19:33.550 --> 19:34.400
We're in a rush.

19:34.400 --> 19:34.880
Okay.

19:41.630 --> 19:42.960
Why is Li Bingyan hiding?

19:42.960 --> 19:44.090
Is she afraid to take responsibility?

19:44.090 --> 19:44.800
Stop shouting!

19:44.800 --> 19:45.470
Calm down!

19:45.550 --> 19:46.510
Everyone, calm down.

19:46.510 --> 19:47.940
-Let's talk this through properly;
don't resort to violence.
-Li Bingyan!

19:47.940 --> 19:48.640
Quiet!

19:48.640 --> 19:49.200
I'm calling the police.

19:49.200 --> 19:50.160
What are you doing?

19:50.160 --> 19:51.110
Be careful.

19:55.590 --> 19:56.350
Keep your voices down.

19:56.350 --> 19:56.920
Stop fighting!

19:56.920 --> 19:59.320
The general manager is here. Stop arguing!

20:06.360 --> 20:07.120
Mr. Ji,

20:07.960 --> 20:08.720
you're finally here.

20:08.720 --> 20:09.480
I've been trying to call Ms. Xu,

20:09.480 --> 20:10.750
but I can't reach her.

20:18.920 --> 20:19.590
Mr. Ji,

20:19.910 --> 20:22.450
I'll have someone arrange
for them to go back and rest.

20:22.450 --> 20:24.140
After all, they are hotel guests.

20:24.140 --> 20:25.960
I will personally investigate
and question them later.

20:25.960 --> 20:27.350
Is that alright with you?

20:27.350 --> 20:28.110
Okay.

20:34.030 --> 20:34.880
Ms. Xu,

20:35.510 --> 20:36.830
with such a major incident happening
in the presidential suite,

20:36.830 --> 20:37.670
where did you go?

20:37.670 --> 20:39.640
Do you know how many people
couldn't reach you?

20:39.640 --> 20:40.110
I went...

20:40.110 --> 20:40.830
Ms. Xu,

20:41.070 --> 20:43.070
we have such important guests
staying in the presidential suite,

20:43.070 --> 20:43.790
yet you

20:43.810 --> 20:45.230
left them behind and ran off.

20:45.230 --> 20:47.160
You made everyone clean up your mess.

20:47.160 --> 20:48.510
As the forewoman of the executive floor,

20:48.510 --> 20:49.570
are you competent?

20:49.790 --> 20:50.350
Mr. Ji,

20:50.680 --> 20:51.350
you really shouldn't have

20:51.350 --> 20:52.160
left such an important guest

20:52.160 --> 20:52.920
in her care.

20:52.920 --> 20:54.320
It's too irresponsible.

20:56.790 --> 20:57.510
Ms. Xu,

20:58.030 --> 20:59.090
your explanation?

20:59.310 --> 21:00.550
Mr. Tan in Room 1810

21:00.550 --> 21:01.880
suddenly went missing.

21:01.880 --> 21:03.610
I took his family to look for him

21:03.680 --> 21:05.110
and temporarily left my post.

21:05.110 --> 21:05.880
I apologize.

21:06.110 --> 21:06.920
Where is he?

21:06.990 --> 21:08.200
He has returned to his room to rest.

21:08.200 --> 21:09.440
Did you arrange a caregiver?

21:09.440 --> 21:10.700
His family is with him.

21:11.020 --> 21:11.880
It's a matter of life and death,

21:11.880 --> 21:13.200
so it's indeed urgent.

21:14.440 --> 21:15.160
Alright, Ms. Lu,

21:15.160 --> 21:16.910
go and comfort the guests first.

21:16.910 --> 21:17.520
Yes,

21:17.540 --> 21:18.540
I'll go right now.

21:21.330 --> 21:22.090
Ms. Xu,

21:27.470 --> 21:28.800
I said it's excusable,

21:29.400 --> 21:31.720
but don't really think
you're not at fault.

21:31.720 --> 21:32.980
You are the forewoman.

21:33.110 --> 21:33.640
Ensuring

21:33.640 --> 21:35.110
the normal operation
of the executive floor

21:35.110 --> 21:36.190
is your duty.

21:36.220 --> 21:37.420
If you fail to do this,

21:37.790 --> 21:38.960
you are derelict in your duty.

21:38.960 --> 21:39.960
In the future, when you encounter

21:39.960 --> 21:41.000
a similar situation,

21:41.000 --> 21:42.860
prepare for both eventualities.

21:43.440 --> 21:44.240
I got it.

21:44.640 --> 21:46.640
I didn't think it through this time.

21:47.260 --> 21:47.980
I'm sorry.

21:48.810 --> 21:50.000
Go deal with it now.

21:50.640 --> 21:51.550
Hurry up.

21:58.440 --> 22:00.200
[Photos and videos]

22:00.260 --> 22:00.440
[Loading]

22:01.570 --> 22:01.750
[Handling]

22:01.840 --> 22:02.180
[Photos and videos]

22:02.300 --> 22:03.880
[It's easier to be recommended
with description.]

22:06.480 --> 22:08.130
[Li Bingyan's security pushing people]

22:09.770 --> 22:11.750
[Li Bingyan's security pushing people,
Qiao Feifei fans being humiliated]

22:15.200 --> 22:16.230
Stop recording!

22:16.230 --> 22:17.500
Why did you push me?

22:19.480 --> 22:21.940
Li Bingyan is going to
be dropped by the show.

22:21.960 --> 22:23.680
This is the internal notice document.

22:23.680 --> 22:25.410
It will be announced this week.

22:28.030 --> 22:29.790
Two of Li Bingyan's brand endorsements

22:29.790 --> 22:31.070
are reportedly going to
be replaced as well.

22:31.070 --> 22:33.470
Her agency is going to
sue our Purong Hotel.

22:33.480 --> 22:34.350
Ms. Xu,

22:34.650 --> 22:35.710
what should we do?

22:35.740 --> 22:37.180
Sue our hotel?

22:37.600 --> 22:38.790
Is it that serious?

22:44.790 --> 22:45.510
Back then,

22:45.510 --> 22:46.790
when I invited Qiao Feifei to stay

22:46.790 --> 22:48.400
at our Purong Hotel,

22:48.510 --> 22:50.510
I waited outside her manager's door,
without food or drink,

22:50.510 --> 22:51.590
for two whole nights.

22:51.590 --> 22:52.650
What did I do it for?

22:53.200 --> 22:54.750
Don't I just want to bring glory

22:54.750 --> 22:56.200
to our Purong Hotel?

22:57.070 --> 22:59.350
It's the critical stage
for sales performance,

22:59.350 --> 23:02.200
yet such a bad incident happened
in the presidential suite.

23:02.200 --> 23:02.960
Ms. Xu,

23:03.510 --> 23:04.000
do you have no sense of responsibility

23:04.000 --> 23:05.680
towards our hotel at all?

23:11.790 --> 23:13.880
I will solve my own problems.

23:14.510 --> 23:16.350
You don't need to
put on a show for others here.

23:16.350 --> 23:17.480
Put on a show?

23:18.270 --> 23:19.200
What do you mean?

23:19.510 --> 23:20.270
Ms. Lu,

23:21.000 --> 23:22.510
go about your business first.

23:22.510 --> 23:23.510
Ms. Xu and I

23:23.790 --> 23:26.450
will discuss the follow-up
work arrangements.

23:27.350 --> 23:28.200
Okay, Mr. Ji.

23:28.680 --> 23:30.210
If you need me later,

23:30.590 --> 23:31.720
I will go all out.

23:41.070 --> 23:42.070
I am sorry, Mr. Ji.

23:42.830 --> 23:43.830
I didn't expect this

23:43.830 --> 23:46.090
would have such a big impact on the hotel.

23:46.240 --> 23:47.550
I will try my best

23:47.550 --> 23:49.000
to solve it.

23:49.240 --> 23:51.030
I will go find Li Bingyan right now.

23:51.030 --> 23:51.850
I'll wait for your results.

23:51.850 --> 23:52.570
Okay.

24:06.720 --> 24:07.440
Hello.

24:07.480 --> 24:08.240
Excuse me,

24:08.350 --> 24:09.830
is Ms. Li Bingyan here?

24:09.880 --> 24:10.740
She is not here.

24:10.960 --> 24:11.880
You are?

24:11.880 --> 24:13.030
I'm her lawyer.

24:13.030 --> 24:14.510
You can tell me anything.

24:14.880 --> 24:15.920
Well,

24:15.950 --> 24:16.920
I would like

24:17.000 --> 24:17.790
to ask

24:17.790 --> 24:19.740
if you could withdraw
the lawsuit against our hotel.

24:19.740 --> 24:21.030
We can discuss

24:21.030 --> 24:21.440
and face any issues together.

24:21.440 --> 24:22.350
Say no more.

24:22.350 --> 24:25.000
Ms. Li Bingyan is currently caught
in a public opinion storm.

24:25.000 --> 24:26.110
She is suffering heavy losses.

24:26.110 --> 24:28.330
She has entrusted me and my legal team

24:28.360 --> 24:30.290
with full authority
to protect her rights and interests.

24:30.290 --> 24:32.620
Your Purong Hotel's poor management

24:32.650 --> 24:34.800
has damaged my client's reputation

24:34.830 --> 24:35.680
and stalled her career.

24:35.680 --> 24:37.510
We are still in the stage of
collecting evidence.

24:37.510 --> 24:39.850
We will contact your hotel's
legal department later.

24:39.850 --> 24:41.240
If you have any questions,

24:41.240 --> 24:43.170
we can communicate at the hearing.

24:43.200 --> 24:43.940
Sir!

24:58.920 --> 25:00.280
[You're my love.]

25:02.000 --> 25:03.160
What's the matter,

25:03.190 --> 25:04.120
Butler Xu?

25:04.140 --> 25:05.350
Hello, David.

25:05.380 --> 25:06.700
It's like this.

25:06.880 --> 25:07.680
What happened yesterday

25:07.680 --> 25:10.070
has gotten out of control on the internet.

25:10.100 --> 25:11.750
I know you have your considerations,

25:11.750 --> 25:13.270
but it has affected our hotel's

25:13.270 --> 25:14.510
normal operation.

25:14.740 --> 25:16.200
The other party wants to sue us.

25:16.200 --> 25:17.240
So,

25:17.240 --> 25:18.000
I want to ask,

25:18.000 --> 25:19.000
can you

25:19.110 --> 25:21.590
ask Feifei to tell her fans

25:21.590 --> 25:24.000
to calm down a little bit?

25:24.020 --> 25:25.150
Calm down?

25:25.180 --> 25:26.380
I'm so angry.

25:26.400 --> 25:27.790
Bullying my fans is bullying me.

25:27.790 --> 25:28.960
I won't give up!

25:28.960 --> 25:29.990
Alright, Feifei.

25:30.010 --> 25:30.790
We have a magazine shoot

25:30.790 --> 25:31.960
this afternoon.

25:31.960 --> 25:33.400
You won't look pretty if you're angry.

25:33.400 --> 25:34.730
Go change your clothes.

25:35.700 --> 25:36.300
Go on.

25:40.110 --> 25:41.610
As for what happened yesterday,

25:41.610 --> 25:42.510
strictly speaking,

25:42.510 --> 25:44.030
it has nothing to do with us.

25:44.030 --> 25:45.680
So we really can't help.

25:46.030 --> 25:46.790
Sorry.

26:02.550 --> 26:03.440
Ms. Xu.

26:04.030 --> 26:04.830
What's wrong?

26:05.080 --> 26:07.560
The guest in 1906 left this for you.

26:09.880 --> 26:11.030
Mr. Tan left?

26:15.680 --> 26:16.550
Mr. Tan!

26:17.240 --> 26:19.430
-The program team has made an appointment.
-Mr. Tan!

26:19.430 --> 26:20.490
Okay, come with me.

26:22.310 --> 26:23.240
Mr. Tan!

26:23.750 --> 26:24.560
Ms. Xu.

26:24.590 --> 26:25.720
I can't accept this.

26:27.250 --> 26:29.580
Do you want to open it
and take a look first?

26:35.490 --> 26:36.960
I got this sample

26:36.960 --> 26:38.110
from a friend.

26:38.130 --> 26:39.200
It's handmade,

26:39.230 --> 26:40.310
and the materials aren't expensive.

26:40.310 --> 26:41.070
I just want to give it to you

26:41.070 --> 26:43.270
to express my feelings.

26:43.310 --> 26:44.970
No pressure this time, right?

26:45.450 --> 26:46.450
It's so beautiful.

26:46.450 --> 26:47.300
Thank you.

26:47.330 --> 26:48.070
I'll accept it.

26:48.070 --> 26:49.200
I'm glad you like it.

26:53.260 --> 26:55.060
There is something in your hair.

26:57.040 --> 26:58.280
I'm sorry.

27:09.830 --> 27:10.480
It's okay.

27:11.550 --> 27:12.570
I'll get going now.

27:12.570 --> 27:13.500
Have a safe trip.

27:14.830 --> 27:15.430
Okay.

27:24.270 --> 27:25.110
Mr. Ji.

27:25.690 --> 27:27.050
Are you done with your work?

27:27.050 --> 27:28.510
I went to look for Li Bingyan just now,

27:28.510 --> 27:29.640
but I didn't see her.

27:29.640 --> 27:30.330
You didn't see her?

27:30.330 --> 27:31.130
And that's it?

27:33.640 --> 27:35.570
Where is your mind at?

27:36.230 --> 27:38.630
Do you only have that one guest
in your eyes?

27:39.700 --> 27:41.330
I just went to see Mr. Tan off.

27:41.390 --> 27:42.160
There's a huge issue

27:42.160 --> 27:43.260
with the presidential suite.

27:43.260 --> 27:44.370
I've always believed in you

27:44.370 --> 27:46.520
and bought you time to solve it.

27:46.550 --> 27:47.240
And look at you.

27:47.240 --> 27:48.700
Instead of hurrying up
to figure something out,

27:48.700 --> 27:50.760
you're receiving gifts from a guest.

27:51.110 --> 27:51.960
Do you think

27:51.960 --> 27:53.110
fawning over one guest all day

27:53.110 --> 27:54.590
will secure your position?

27:54.590 --> 27:56.560
There are plenty of people
waiting to take your spot.

27:56.560 --> 27:58.140
Tell me if you want to quit.

28:34.240 --> 28:34.750
Why did you...

28:34.750 --> 28:35.590
Ms. Li!

28:35.750 --> 28:36.790
Ms. Li!

28:38.270 --> 28:39.240
Ms. Li,

28:40.510 --> 28:42.350
I am here on behalf of Purong Hotel.

28:42.350 --> 28:45.070
I request that you withdraw
the lawsuit against our hotel.

28:45.070 --> 28:47.030
Let's face the media together.

28:47.030 --> 28:47.590
okay?

28:47.790 --> 28:48.510
We?

28:50.550 --> 28:52.030
Is there a common ground

28:52.030 --> 28:53.440
between you and me?

28:54.880 --> 28:56.630
We are your service provider.

28:56.650 --> 28:57.510
We have always

28:57.510 --> 29:00.120
handled problems from your perspective.

29:00.150 --> 29:02.000
What's more, during this period,

29:02.000 --> 29:04.190
haven't we been getting along well?

29:04.850 --> 29:06.270
Playing the emotional card?

29:06.270 --> 29:07.930
Please take a good look at the target.

29:07.930 --> 29:09.960
There is only an employment relationship
between us,

29:09.960 --> 29:11.440
not a friendship.

29:11.710 --> 29:14.190
Your hotel provided hellish service.

29:14.210 --> 29:16.670
Now that something went wrong,
you still want me to be lenient?

29:16.670 --> 29:18.060
What a joke.

29:18.270 --> 29:19.440
Ms. Li,

29:20.270 --> 29:21.790
right after the incident,

29:21.790 --> 29:23.070
the hotel sent security personnel

29:23.070 --> 29:24.350
to handle the situation.

29:24.350 --> 29:25.310
Besides,

29:25.310 --> 29:27.480
it wasn't the hotel
you actually clashed with,

29:27.480 --> 29:31.070
but the fans who trespassed onto
the presidential suite floor.

29:31.200 --> 29:32.200
Logically speaking,

29:32.200 --> 29:34.100
you shouldn't be suing the hotel.

29:34.120 --> 29:35.430
Of course, I understand

29:35.430 --> 29:38.170
that the agency wants to
use the hotel as a megaphone

29:38.170 --> 29:39.930
to amplify this matter.

29:41.360 --> 29:42.430
What do you mean?

29:42.450 --> 29:44.370
Are you making excuses to shift the blame?

29:44.370 --> 29:45.920
Your hotel's management loopholes

29:45.920 --> 29:47.450
caused such a huge conflict

29:47.460 --> 29:49.320
and damaged my reputation.

29:49.340 --> 29:51.860
Now you want to wash your hands of it

29:52.030 --> 29:53.960
and avoid taking responsibility?

29:57.550 --> 29:58.610
And another thing.

29:59.180 --> 30:01.250
You're just a floor forewoman.

30:01.420 --> 30:03.880
How can you talk to me
about an equal position?

30:03.880 --> 30:05.240
Who do you think you are?

30:05.240 --> 30:06.720
Getting along well?

30:06.720 --> 30:07.720
Do you deserve it?

30:08.070 --> 30:09.730
Go back and tell your general manager

30:09.730 --> 30:11.590
to get the best lawyer right away.

30:11.850 --> 30:12.720
Let's

30:13.350 --> 30:14.510
see in court.

30:15.940 --> 30:16.740
Wait a minute!

30:19.200 --> 30:19.960
Ms. Li.

30:21.270 --> 30:23.200
Do I need to remind you?

30:23.270 --> 30:24.200
A couple of days ago,

30:24.200 --> 30:26.680
when they were filming
at the VIP entrance,

30:26.680 --> 30:28.240
you intentionally brought your boyfriend

30:28.240 --> 30:29.770
and showed up there, right?

30:29.960 --> 30:31.510
I reminded you the day before

30:31.510 --> 30:32.590
that during that time,

30:32.590 --> 30:34.750
the program crew
will be filming at the VIP entrance,

30:34.750 --> 30:35.980
and there will be media.

30:35.980 --> 30:38.640
But you just had to
show up at that specific time.

30:38.830 --> 30:41.110
Didn't you just use me, a lowly forewoman,

30:41.110 --> 30:42.270
to get the information,

30:42.270 --> 30:43.550
then direct and act in

30:43.550 --> 30:45.590
an attention-grabbing drama,

30:45.590 --> 30:48.070
and finally push the responsibility
for poor arrangements

30:48.070 --> 30:49.890
onto our hotel?

30:49.910 --> 30:50.910
Isn't that right?

30:51.510 --> 30:52.530
What are you trying to say?

30:52.530 --> 30:54.470
That being troubled by Qiao Feifei's fans

30:54.470 --> 30:55.790
is my own fault?

30:56.510 --> 30:57.840
That's not what I meant.

30:58.000 --> 30:59.440
I came to see you today

30:59.470 --> 31:01.210
not to discuss who is right or wrong,

31:01.210 --> 31:03.270
but to ask you to rationally consider

31:03.280 --> 31:04.680
your current situation.

31:06.510 --> 31:06.960
Right.

31:07.170 --> 31:09.150
Although I am just a lowly forewoman,

31:09.150 --> 31:10.520
on an executive level,

31:10.540 --> 31:12.270
I am the spokesperson for the hotel.

31:12.270 --> 31:14.270
Today I'm here on behalf of the hotel

31:14.270 --> 31:16.230
to discuss a way forward with you.

31:16.400 --> 31:17.420
In short,

31:17.510 --> 31:19.830
if you withdraw
the lawsuit against the hotel,

31:19.830 --> 31:22.070
the rewards you receive
will be substantial.

31:22.070 --> 31:23.750
The hotel won't have to put more energy

31:23.750 --> 31:26.130
into dealing with
this unreasonable lawsuit.

31:26.130 --> 31:26.890
Then,

31:26.910 --> 31:28.260
we can definitely,

31:28.310 --> 31:30.880
with the attitude
and sincerity of an ally,

31:30.880 --> 31:33.830
help defend you in public

31:33.830 --> 31:35.460
and recover your losses.

31:35.590 --> 31:36.400
However,

31:36.720 --> 31:39.430
if you fail to appreciate
the hotel's good intentions

31:39.430 --> 31:41.040
and choose to bite
the hand that feeds you,

31:41.040 --> 31:43.310
then this lawsuit
is bound to be a protracted one.

31:43.310 --> 31:44.900
And both sides will suffer.

31:44.930 --> 31:47.680
Setting aside our hotel's losses,

31:48.030 --> 31:49.790
during this time,

31:50.110 --> 31:52.890
you may face a damaged reputation,

31:52.910 --> 31:54.540
career stagnation,

31:54.570 --> 31:56.420
and fleeting popularity.

31:56.510 --> 31:58.310
How quickly
the entertainment industry changes,

31:58.310 --> 32:00.310
I think you know better than anyone.

32:00.440 --> 32:01.070
So,

32:01.350 --> 32:03.270
whether to cooperate with us or not,

32:03.270 --> 32:05.130
think clearly before you decide.

32:28.480 --> 32:30.440
You're just a floor forewoman.

32:30.460 --> 32:32.990
How can you talk to me
about a common position?

32:33.230 --> 32:34.560
Who do you think you are?

32:34.590 --> 32:36.000
Getting along happily?

32:36.000 --> 32:37.030
Do you deserve it?

32:49.510 --> 32:50.310
Ms. Xu,

32:50.590 --> 32:51.590
you impress me.

32:52.590 --> 32:54.110
Li Bingyan's legal representative

32:54.110 --> 32:55.090
sent me an email,

32:55.720 --> 32:57.030
saying their internal team

32:57.030 --> 32:59.760
needs to reconsider
the litigation resolution.

33:00.270 --> 33:02.340
It seems your persuasion worked.

33:02.440 --> 33:03.200
Good job.

33:05.030 --> 33:05.790
That's good.

33:09.350 --> 33:10.350
Mr. Ji is not here.

33:10.590 --> 33:11.920
Are you looking for him?

33:12.200 --> 33:12.960
No.

33:14.350 --> 33:15.510
Regarding the hotel's losses,

33:15.510 --> 33:17.200
Mr. Ji has already gone
to figure out a way.

33:17.200 --> 33:19.310
He will bring the program team's
accommodation orders

33:19.310 --> 33:20.400
to the hotel

33:20.510 --> 33:22.790
to try to eliminate the negative impact.

33:24.350 --> 33:25.440
This matter

33:25.680 --> 33:27.240
is considered over.

33:27.350 --> 33:29.310
You don't need to blame yourself too much.

33:29.310 --> 33:31.070
After all, you were also drawn into

33:31.070 --> 33:32.830
this intrigue.

33:32.880 --> 33:34.440
You handled it very well.

33:35.440 --> 33:36.590
In the HSKP Department,

33:36.590 --> 33:38.730
it's inevitable to encounter such things.

33:38.730 --> 33:40.480
Even if you are promoted in the future,

33:40.480 --> 33:41.480
some things

33:41.590 --> 33:43.600
will still require you
to handle them personally.

33:43.600 --> 33:46.030
Consider this a trial.

33:47.680 --> 33:48.880
Thank you, Mr. Xue.

33:50.200 --> 33:51.300
I'll go back to work then.

33:51.300 --> 33:51.860
Okay.

34:10.020 --> 34:12.670
[HSKP Department of Purong Hotel ,Xu Miyu]

35:06.360 --> 35:07.500
Li Bingyan has yielded.

35:07.500 --> 35:08.670
Ms. Xu got it done.

35:23.770 --> 35:24.630
Do you think

35:24.630 --> 35:25.760
fawning over one guest all day

35:25.760 --> 35:27.290
will secure your position?

35:27.380 --> 35:29.160
There are plenty of people
waiting to take your spot.

35:29.160 --> 35:30.000
If you want to quit,

35:30.000 --> 35:30.880
tell me sooner.

35:49.560 --> 35:51.370
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

35:53.070 --> 35:54.710
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

35:56.930 --> 35:58.840
♪ People in the city ♪

35:59.660 --> 36:02.600
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

36:04.530 --> 36:06.340
♪ The palms of time ♪

36:08.240 --> 36:11.380
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

36:11.990 --> 36:14.910
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

36:15.910 --> 36:17.950
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

36:20.510 --> 36:23.220
It was indeed my fault to begin with.

36:22.220 --> 36:24.700
[Civil Complaint]

36:23.320 --> 36:25.110
I had some conflicts with the hotel,

36:25.110 --> 36:26.400
which led to some misunderstandings,

36:26.400 --> 36:28.480
and even alerted the company's legal team.

36:28.480 --> 36:29.800
Thinking about it now,

36:32.400 --> 36:33.860
I am truly ashamed.

36:37.410 --> 36:38.340
Mr. Ji.

36:40.190 --> 36:40.920
Bingyan,

36:41.190 --> 36:42.230
long time no see.

36:42.230 --> 36:43.400
Long time no see.

36:46.070 --> 36:48.030
Regarding the extreme behavior
of those fans,

36:48.030 --> 36:49.110
the fan club has already stepped in

36:49.110 --> 36:50.190
and severely criticized them.

36:50.190 --> 36:51.030
Thank you.

36:51.490 --> 36:52.140
Here.

36:58.810 --> 36:59.510
Mr. Dai,

36:59.510 --> 37:01.310
thank you for your cooperation.

37:01.440 --> 37:03.240
You are a reasonable man, Mr. Ji.

37:03.510 --> 37:04.800
Technically speaking,

37:04.800 --> 37:07.510
the troublemaking fans
are not part of our company.

37:07.510 --> 37:10.370
This time, we are willing to cooperate
in mediation

37:10.400 --> 37:12.030
purely out of respect for Mr. Ji.

37:12.030 --> 37:12.630
Thank you.

37:13.150 --> 37:15.550
But there is one thing I must make clear.

37:18.550 --> 37:19.510
Please go ahead.

37:20.130 --> 37:21.220
I heard that

37:21.320 --> 37:22.400
these fans went up

37:22.400 --> 37:23.190
with a guest

37:23.190 --> 37:25.440
who previously stayed
in the presidential suite.

37:25.440 --> 37:26.510
the presidential suite.

37:26.510 --> 37:26.920
Yes.

37:26.920 --> 37:28.630
We have checked the surveillance video.

37:28.630 --> 37:29.630
Then,

37:30.110 --> 37:31.640
how do they know each other?

37:35.240 --> 37:36.320
I also heard

37:36.410 --> 37:37.770
that the person who introduced them

37:37.770 --> 37:40.440
was the VIP manager
of your sales department—

37:40.510 --> 37:41.400
Lu Zhenzhen.

37:43.110 --> 37:44.640
I've dealt with her before.

37:45.320 --> 37:46.910
As long as it benefits her,

37:46.930 --> 37:47.590
she would certainly

37:47.590 --> 37:48.920
do something like this.

37:52.970 --> 37:55.620
[General Manager's Office]

37:59.660 --> 38:01.020
Mr. Ji,

38:01.860 --> 38:04.520
do I need to communicate with
Li Bingyan's side?

38:05.840 --> 38:09.040
How did Qiao Feifei's fans
get to the presidential suite?

38:09.080 --> 38:10.120
I have no idea.

38:10.150 --> 38:11.480
Didn't they come to you?

38:11.510 --> 38:13.590
Weren't you the person
in charge of the fan meeting?

38:13.590 --> 38:14.280
Mr. Ji,

38:14.280 --> 38:16.480
they asked me about Mr. Duan Jr.

38:16.480 --> 38:16.880
I was also...

38:16.880 --> 38:18.190
Did they ask about it

38:18.360 --> 38:20.000
or did you leak it on purpose?

38:20.020 --> 38:21.750
Of course they asked.

38:22.030 --> 38:24.520
Leaking a guest's information privately
is a serious dereliction of duty.

38:24.520 --> 38:26.240
Are you clear on how it should be handled

38:26.240 --> 38:28.070
according to industry regulations?

38:28.070 --> 38:29.510
I'm sorry, Mr. Ji.

38:29.630 --> 38:32.150
I was really pushed too far by them

38:32.170 --> 38:33.630
and acted without thinking.

38:33.630 --> 38:34.800
Mr. Ji, you must give me a chance

38:34.800 --> 38:36.280
to make up for it.

38:36.300 --> 38:38.260
I happen to have a few major clients

38:38.290 --> 38:39.410
about to close.

38:39.430 --> 38:40.840
I promise that this quarter,

38:40.840 --> 38:43.700
I can bring at least
three large orders to the hotel.

38:46.310 --> 38:48.510
Your bonus for one quarter
will be deducted.

38:48.510 --> 38:50.630
You said three large orders yourself.

38:50.630 --> 38:52.030
If you can't do it, you'll be fired.

38:52.030 --> 38:52.670
Also,

38:52.920 --> 38:54.900
I don't know what your habits were before,

38:54.900 --> 38:55.820
but here,

38:55.890 --> 38:57.890
stop playing dirty

38:57.910 --> 38:59.230
and taking shortcuts.

39:00.030 --> 39:01.030
Mr. Ji, I know I was wrong.

39:01.030 --> 39:02.550
I will never do it again.

39:11.510 --> 39:12.440
Mr. Zhao,

39:12.470 --> 39:14.910
Purong Hotel is certainly very sincere.

39:14.940 --> 39:16.980
[Customer information
Yinhe Zhichuang Exhibition Planning Group]

39:15.960 --> 39:16.840
As for the specific terms,

39:16.840 --> 39:19.100
how about we set up
a time to meet and talk?

39:19.320 --> 39:21.000
Tomorrow is fine for me, of course.

39:21.000 --> 39:21.600
Zhenzhen.

39:24.950 --> 39:25.720
Mr. Zhao,

39:25.740 --> 39:29.120
how about I visit your company personally
tomorrow afternoon?

39:29.120 --> 39:30.230
Don't you know me?

39:30.230 --> 39:31.700
We've known each other for so long.

39:31.700 --> 39:33.550
I will definitely give you the best plan.

39:33.550 --> 39:34.400
Zhenzhen.

39:37.190 --> 39:37.840
Okay.

39:38.190 --> 39:40.050
Okay, Mr. Zhao, see you tomorrow.

39:44.170 --> 39:45.180
[Approval] [Lu Zhenzhen's outing request]

39:46.960 --> 39:48.320
Why did you drink so much?

39:48.320 --> 39:50.120
Didn't you see I was on the phone?

39:51.400 --> 39:52.510
I had a social engagement tonight.

39:52.510 --> 39:53.910
I drank a little too much.

39:54.310 --> 39:55.970
Then you should get some rest.

39:56.150 --> 39:57.990
I still have to work overtime for a while.

39:57.990 --> 39:59.550
Can you cook some porridge for me?

39:59.550 --> 40:00.940
My stomach is not feeling well.

40:00.940 --> 40:02.370
Can you just order some takeout yourself?

40:02.370 --> 40:05.030
Won't the takeout be cold
by the time it arrives?

40:06.670 --> 40:07.440
Nie Yucheng,

40:09.410 --> 40:11.200
I'm not your mother.

40:11.310 --> 40:12.680
Ji Feng keeps an eye on me every day now.

40:12.680 --> 40:14.610
I'm under a lot of pressure at work.

40:14.730 --> 40:16.960
If you think I can't serve you well,

40:16.990 --> 40:18.450
I'll get you a nanny, okay?

40:21.230 --> 40:21.800
Okay.

40:21.800 --> 40:23.260
You get back to work. Okay.

40:26.630 --> 40:28.960
The medicine is in the living room drawer.

40:38.870 --> 40:39.760
Hurry, give me the bowl.

40:39.760 --> 40:40.760
It smells so good.

40:41.960 --> 40:44.400
This is the newly arrived
Nanhui salted meat.

40:44.400 --> 40:45.800
The quality is excellent.

40:45.800 --> 40:47.860
Judging by your look, it's in the bag.

40:48.250 --> 40:49.850
It's almost a done deal.

40:51.570 --> 40:52.970
Have a taste. How is it?

40:53.000 --> 40:54.070
Thank you.

40:56.150 --> 40:56.670
Wait.

40:58.070 --> 40:59.400
I suggest

40:59.400 --> 41:01.190
you take a sip of soup first

41:01.220 --> 41:02.970
to open up your taste buds,

41:02.990 --> 41:04.070
and then eat the food.

41:04.070 --> 41:05.070
So particular.

41:05.360 --> 41:06.960
Alright, I'll listen to you.

41:11.400 --> 41:12.670
You should taste it first.

41:12.670 --> 41:14.710
Your head is almost
falling into the soup bowl.

41:14.710 --> 41:15.360
No, no, no.

41:15.550 --> 41:17.110
You... you taste it first.

41:24.510 --> 41:25.840
How is it?

41:28.670 --> 41:30.000
Is it not good?

41:32.280 --> 41:33.080
Let me taste it.
